tests.comment: Runs very well at average 34 frames per second with my current hardware and settings. Some textures are deformed including guardians, divine beasts, and a few more. Everything else works just fine, so you can still have a ton of fun while you wait for those few bugs to be fixed. Keep in mind often the game will not boot unless you delete the vulkan shaders cache.
tests.author: Durocks

tests.comment: Runs very well. Guardians, divine beasts, chests, and others are not being rendered, making them invisible. So you can't finish the game. Also sometimes the game will not boot unless you delete the shaders cache.
